### **How to Use the New Click CLI:**

**Basic Commands:**
```powershell
# Create a K2SHBWI file from image
python tools/cli_click.py create diagram.png output.k2sh -t "My Diagram" --auto-hotspots

# Get file information
python tools/cli_click.py info output.k2sh --list-hotspots

# Validate file
python tools/cli_click.py validate output.k2sh

# View the file
python tools/cli_click.py view output.k2sh --web

# Convert HTML to K2SHBWI
python tools/cli_click.py convert presentation.html output.k2sh -f html

# Batch convert directory
python tools/cli_click.py batch ./presentations -f pptx -o ./output -r
```

